{"tid":256131,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"飲開伯爵紅茶(earl grey)茶包既巴打入一入黎","createTime":"2017-05-24T10:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T18:51:16.000Z","uid":90866,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89a857a8af7314a6e12d74f6a2de68c4bb9f034f","tid":256131,"uid":90866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"一直飲開百佳買既twinings,感覺都唔差。但係cafe飲過1次另一款茶包後，發現正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我對質素既要求唔係好高，所以有無識貨之人可以推薦下70~150蚊，容易買到，又屌打到twinings既茶包牌子就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/180049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F180049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8f70b7f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"197f7e10707fa6c30a65cc174e1ceaad2e0cacb4","tid":256131,"uid":17324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"馬莎  鐵罐金裝"},{"pid":"7389f591586bddabe0d0f792c530a664c9eb891e","tid":256131,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"Fortnum &amp; Mason"},{"pid":"655ed3763800c9259747b1ebcb0eeb6ccfa73dac","tid":256131,"uid":90866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T23:22:48.000Z","msg":"多謝曬巴打既推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da502754ac9e17df26c1e22cc4e6bba0e6067cf","tid":256131,"uid":27970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"Fortnum &amp; Mason"},{"pid":"5f72431bcd1f30cb9a5894ac35312327f19d5d6f","tid":256131,"uid":35971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"twinings 好易上隠"},{"pid":"962eb614561f823b325b6283c42f935d2b7338a3","tid":256131,"uid":43304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":